atmbranchfinderspring.resourceserver.authentication

Class ExpiredTokenCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • atmbranchfinderspring.resourceserver.authentication.ExpiredTokenCollector

  • @Component
public class ExpiredTokenCollector
extends java.lang.Object
    ExpiredTokenCollector is a helper object that spawns a seperate Thread where it periodically goes through the AccessTokenRepository to check if any access token are expired. If they are expired, it deletes them.
